    { name: "Benztropine (Cogentin) IM/IV", type: "Anticholinergic", action: "Blocks central muscarinic receptors and inhibits dopamine reuptake, restoring basal ganglia neurotransmitter balance", sideEffects: "Dry mouth, constipation, urinary retention, blurred vision, confusion", contra: "Narrow-angle glaucoma, GI obstruction, dementia", pearl: "Alternative first-line for acute dystonic reaction; give 1-2mg IM or IV; longer duration of action than diphenhydramine; continue oral dosing to prevent recurrence" }
